Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You should smell the lily, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NSniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,All set, are you girls ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.47,0:00:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Try to smile pretty for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,but also, we loved you from\Nthe beginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,so we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I had to have you all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:30.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NDelicious smell. Slurp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kureha.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:24.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl. Lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, you're close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Wait a minute.\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NHeh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously! Why are you\Nin my house again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I moved in, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl! All done!\NWe're finished moving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,We're your roomies, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Bottoms up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NNew roomie noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Bottoms up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU, GINKO]\NNew roomie noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Get... out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Get out of my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to leave, and,\Nby the way, it's not acceptable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.02,Main,,0,0,0,,to just move into someone's\Nhouse without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:30.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl. But, Kure-pie,\Nyou ate your new roomie noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,So? I don't even get\Nwhat that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A]\NLook, it's that one girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B]\NWha--? Oh, her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.24,Main,,0,0,0,,She's totally bad luck\Nto her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT C]\NIt's worse than bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Students are disappearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,and the missing girls all\Nhappen to be from her class!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NThere, you heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Getting close to me is bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get caught\Nup in the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:05:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.68,Main,,0,0,0,,If you two make friends with me,\Nyou'll just wind up excluded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.68,Main,,0,0,0,,because that's\Nthe law of this herd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone,\Nfor your own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:17.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl! You're the one\Nwho doesn't understand, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu told you, Ginko\Nand Lulu came here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.28,Main,,0,0,0,,to make friends with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] We'll protect Kureha\Nfrom the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:29.45,Main,,0,0,0,,And we promise, we won't\Nback down on love. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I'm not lying! She was\Na bear masquerading as a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NThat's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko turned into a bear\Nright in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,She ate Sumika.\NShe killed my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko told me as much herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,And then... And then, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:01.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I took my gun and\NI aimed it right at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NKureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,That's enough of this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You poor darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,The shock was just too much,\Nso you've clearly hallucinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's real! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't force you to\Ndo anything right away;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.29,Main,,0,0,0,,however, you will eventually\Nneed to accept the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,of the situation and let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Next Sunday is your\Nbirthday. It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia's little girl about\Nto be 17. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Time certainly flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,So, tell me, what would\Nyou like to do this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Go out for dinner? Or did you\Nwant a particular present?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NNo, not this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NNow that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,you know your mother's pendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,She loved it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a present for her\Nwhen she turned seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm actually the one\Nwho gave it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, it was from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Yes. It was a symbol\Nof a promise between friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:05.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We pledged to each other that\Nwe would never forget love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You pledged to\Nnever forget love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,We sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as you\Ndon't forget love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.31,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll never, ever\Nbe truly alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,And, if you don't\Ngive up on love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,even if you lose something,\Nyou'll never be invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's\Nimportant to know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,that love can cause\Nus pain, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,For example, when we\Nremember time that's been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Remember time that's been lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Whenever we feel that pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,we should try to focus\Non something else
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,and not be too hard\Non ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I think what you\Nprobably need right now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:52.31,Main,,0,0,0,,more than anything\Nis a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,A new friend? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Try allowing yourself to\Nget close to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get\Nclose to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika is my only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never give up on love,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU, GINKO]\NGrowl, growl, munch, munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl, munch, munch.\NGrowl, growl, munch, munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NMunch, munch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl. Kure-pie is eating\None of those rolls again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but Lulu doesn't think they\Nsmell all that delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha eats what\Ntastes like love to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,What tastes like love?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's something\Nwhich can't be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,by any storm, or bear, or human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Say what? Are you sure\Nthat's for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NIt's real. I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NIt's okay. I'm your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nbe alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm here, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NLady Kumaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I remember\Ngetting love from someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I came.\NWhy I crossed the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:36.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha, I want to have you.\NI want you all to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NHey, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Got a sec, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA] I want you to know\Nwe talked it over this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone agreed\Nwe've been really cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,We know we're in the wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,and we're beyond sorry\Nfor what we've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,So, we wanna\Nmake it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Not just you,\Nto Sumika, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You all excluded Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,None of you have the\Nright to be forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Why the change of heart now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:18.91,Main,,0,0,0,,If this is some sort of game,\Nyou girls better finish it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,because I won't lose\Nto people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna\Nmake me invisible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, please forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.21,Main,,0,0,0,,We've all been so--\NWe've been so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[cyring] We really are sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NWhat was that, growl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Only we get to make\Nfriends with Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.85,0:10:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl is in\Nour way, big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Only one solution.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl. Hey! Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.37,Main,,0,0,0,,"Article One:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,The Way to a Girl's Heart\Nis Through Her Stomach."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Challenge accepted! Ginko and\NLulu are going to make Kure-pie
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.71,0:11:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,something she loves as\Nmuch as those crazy rolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,And then--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu is so clever! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,No! You can't transform here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter\Nhow hungry you may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to follow\Ncourt rules on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,We're only allowed to eat the\Nflesh of invisible girls, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,So, do you know what kinds\Nof food Kure-pie likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:33.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NShiokara and spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds like what\Nan old man would eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,She's liked them\Nsince she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:41.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm. All right, guess we know\Nwhat tonight's dinner will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!\NWelcome home, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUm, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NMaking dinner. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:58.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko and Lulu have decided\Nto make your love flavor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Make what? My "love flavor"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:05.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep! We're cooking\Nyour two favorite foods!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:07.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Yes! We call it\N"Shiokara Spaghetti"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Delicious smell! Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:16.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,A flavor pairing made in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Try one, Ginko!\NCherry tomato! "Ahh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NAhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Here comes, Ginko. Try some\Ncreamy honey flan. "Ahhh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NAhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Eat this, Ginko, creamy,\Nlightly salted salmon! "Ahhh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NAhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NNow it's your turn, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ahhh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:44.43,Main,,0,0,0,,No, thanks. I won't eat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:45.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,But why? We thought you were\Na fan of shiokara and spaghetti
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:55.73,Main,,0,0,0,,just like old men are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, how'd you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,We... didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm certain I only ever\Ntold Sumika about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Two transfer students\Nshouldn't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:08.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Mmm. Good point.\NWe don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm serious. I want you\Nto stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Growl! But we want to\Nbe your friends, Kure-pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:15.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is that so hard\Nto understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Enough about being\Nmy friend! I'm sick of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone trying to\Nmake me give up on my love?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:26.39,Main,,0,0,0,,How many times do I\Nhave to repeat myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want new friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika is my only love!\NI don't want anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you so damn\Ndesperate to get close to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[water dripping]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That was super scary for Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu thought for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.99,Main,,0,0,0,,you were about to tell Kure-pie\Nthe truth about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.33,Main,,0,0,0,,But you know, Ginko,\Nif you tell her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,we can't be human girls anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are the court's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Lulu hopes\NKure-pie remembers you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.67,Main,,0,0,0,,This is getting exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:01.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NGinko, I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Yuri amore! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I just had a hard\Ntime admitting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.\NIt's okay. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.65,Main,,0,0,0,,if we took some time to\Nwash each other all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,It might give us the chance to\Nreally get to know one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Gorgeous smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What about that, Ginko?\NDoes it feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. Yeah, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:42.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And here, Ginko, this spot?\NDoes it feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. It does. Really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And what about here. How does\Nthis spot feel? Really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] Oh, yeah.\NReally good. It's-It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[moaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:14:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,--Uh?\N--There you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.19,Main,,0,0,0,,clean as a whistle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:03.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NHere, Kureha. For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NI know it's a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,My birthday isn't for\Na while, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NYeah, of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't explain it. I just\Nhad to give you this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NOkay. You are so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUm, wait. Don't open it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:33.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.93,Main,,0,0,0,,On your birthday, I want you\Nto come to this spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,then you can read what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Why then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.98,Main,,0,0,0,,So that it's perfect,\Nsince it's my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You got me a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.11,Main,,0,0,0,,How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait though to open it? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:50.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NLook at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:51.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NSuch a beautiful smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I want you to always\Nsmile like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Like a flower. That's my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.92,Main,,0,0,0,,It's funny, even if I had\Nto watch you from a distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I would be happy\Njust to see that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no distance between us.\NI'm always right by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You kept your promise, and\Ndidn't back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never, ever\Nforget that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NThey'll bloom soon, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NOh, Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You're my only friend,\Nand the only friend I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,The flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:41.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA] We asked the school\Nto help you grow flowers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about what\Nhappened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We all really are sorry, Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,The Invisible Storm\Nwrecked this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,but we want to fix it now.\NWe'll do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Our thought was to\Nrefill it with flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,We were hoping we\Ncould work together
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,to make Sumika's\Nlast wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:02.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Last wish? What do\Nyou know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:05.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA] Well, we know it\Nhas to do with your birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.61,Main,,0,0,0,,which is next week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NYeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, I heard\Nthat before, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,before what happened to Sumika\Nhappened, that she said, um.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.91,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,One for you. And she wanted\Nit in a garden full of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:25.67,Main,,0,0,0,,So that it's perfect,\Nsince it's my present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NWe're asking you to allow Us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.01,Main,,0,0,0,,to celebrate your\Nbirthday this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Because that...\NThat's what Sumika wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NPlease, for Sumika's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl! What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko and Lulu are her friends,\Nnot those stinky girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You agree, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA] We don't have much\Ntime before Kureha's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's start today, okay, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS]\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Ladies, thank you for working\Nso hard these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of everyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki has\Nstarted to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,that we are interested\Nin being her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,We only need to endure\Nher a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:53.88,Main,,0,0,0,,At this moment, we will\Nconfirm our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,and make a final decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Who is the evil we must exclude?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:12.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NSelect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,We have chosen Kureha Tsubaki\Nas the evil to exclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:18.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl.\NThis is great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Turns out she is\Nan invisible girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Meaning we can\Neat her, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess who'll be judged\Nthis time. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NLet the Yuri Trial begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish to eat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That way I can save Kureha\Nfrom the Invisible Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Not this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:43.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but doesn't everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,want to protect\Nthe girl they love?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Meh, I wouldn't be too certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] Defendant bears, so\Nfar you've eaten several humans
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.61,Main,,0,0,0,,affiliated with this\N"Invisible Storm,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,all in the name of\N"saving Kureha Tsubaki."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NThey're guilty, Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, answer this\Nquestion honestly, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,And don't say to save Kureha.\NThat's just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, isn't it true,\Nall you really want
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,is to make sure you are Kureha\NTsubaki's one and only friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY]\NObjection! Speculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,The prosecutor is being\Nruled by his personal sadism!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,For your information,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko just wants to give back\Nthe love she got from Kure-pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.77,Main,,0,0,0,,She wants a Promise Kiss.\NIs that so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NOrder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,The objection is overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, please answer\Nthe prosecutor's question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. The truth is. I want\Nto have Kureha all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to be friends\Nwith her again,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,and I want to have\NKureha's love again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the only\Nreason I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the reason\NI crossed the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,and dragged Lulu\Ninto it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,But, Ginko, Lulu wanted\Nto cross the wall with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:57.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, though!\NI won't back down on love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:01.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll still do whatever\Nit takes for love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything.\NThere's no going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I've committed a serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, Ginko? What "serious\Ncrime" do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:15.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! No need to finish\Nthat sentence, okay? Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.86,Main,,0,0,0,,This is too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, the defendant\Nbear confessed in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.78,Main,,0,0,0,,She just admitted\Nto committing a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.74,Main,,0,0,0,,You must find her\Nguilty at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] Ginko Yurishiro,\Nis your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYou bet it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:36.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] And what if\Nit's an egotistical love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:39.13,Main,,0,0,0,,What if that pride\Neventually destroys you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] That's fine,\Nbecause I'm a criminal bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:47.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Defendant bears, I ask you.\NDo you want to be invisible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:49.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Or, would you rather eat humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Guh, bring on the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NGrowl, growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.86,0:21:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] I am now ready\Nto declare the verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuri approved!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you wanna\Nmeet me for? It's kinda late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. This is about Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko and Lulu are going\Nto be friends with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is that\Nsupposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:17.38,Main,,0,0,0,,It means we won't let\Nyou have your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,We're on to you.\NSo now, you disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] No! This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.89,0:22:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you two what I think?\NNo. You just can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl. But we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,We're bears, and we'll\Neat you up, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA]\NAh! Help! Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[roar]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:46.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,One bear successfully\Neliminated by our trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:56.58,Main,,0,0,0,,We know what you two really\Nare, and this is what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:57.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.88,0:23:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HARISHIMA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.93,0:23:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NKureha.
